HEADWORD: lance corporal
<hw>lance" cor`por*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A <er>lancepesade</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An enlisted member of the United States Marine Corps
