[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The lowest rank of corporal; -- a term used in the
British military.</def> <au>RHUD</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lance fish</ent>⟦br⟧
